{"tid":1235752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★David Webb籲「沽空」林鄭　目標價為零","createTime":"2019-06-17T08:42:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T13:52:37.000Z","uid":19454,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"af3ee4e8263796c56e99fec50f6533f7aade7695","tid":1235752,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:42:08.000Z","msg":"特區政府宣布暫緩修訂《逃犯條例》，惟獨立股評人David Webb「未收貨」，發表網誌直言特首林鄭月娥必須下台，認為北京表面上會繼續撐林鄭，但她連任已是不可能的事。<br />\n<br />\nDavid Webb周六發表有關網誌，直指無論如何粉飾《逃犯條例》，亦無助改變內地司法制度之不公平﹙unfairness﹚，而歷史文件亦清楚顯示，將其排除於現時的逃犯條例安排，並非漏洞或錯誤，而是對一國兩制模式之必要。<br />\n<br />\nDavid Webb又指，今屆立法會會期至2020年7月，在此之前，林鄭月娥如果嘗試推進《條例》二讀，形同政治自殺。因此，David Webb預期，條例將擱置到2020年7月後，與23條立法一樣，置於政府「長遠要做」的名單中。<br />\n<br />\nDavid Webb續分析道，林鄭已失去公眾的信任，連任已是不可能的事，還比喻稱如果林鄭是一隻股票，建議沽空她，目標價為零，更取名為「Carrie Trade」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/341353/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-david-webb%E7%B1%B2-%E6%B2%BD%E7%A9%BA-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD-%E7%9B%AE%E6%A8%99%E5%83%B9%E7%82%BA%E9%9B%B6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E8%25A8%258A%2F341353%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-david-webb%25E7%25B1%25B2-%25E6%25B2%25BD%25E7%25A9%25BA-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD-%25E7%259B%25AE%25E6%25A8%2599%25E5%2583%25B9%25E7%2582%25BA%25E9%259B%25B6&d=goC%2B%2BwCxwRgX8SEPTes0u%2FMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=a39bfe5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/341353/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-david-webb%E7%B1%B2-%E6%B2%BD%E7%A9%BA-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD-%E7%9B%AE%E6%A8%99%E5%83%B9%E7%82%BA%E9%9B%B6</a>"},{"pid":"d3c0c36dac775af895138ed668be974fcd83d489","tid":1235752,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:42:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2921033/org/a2cb59e7b16d0062b6033d6e3440864a.jpg/6eLm-qOn9VQMVh9